There are two types of jobs that you can submit:   Shared : a shared job (as the name suggests) is one that shares a node with other jobs.  This is the default and preferred method.  Exclusive : an exclusive job gets a single (or multiple) nodes to itself.  Given this exclusivity, this type of job must know how 
   to use multiple CPUs as most HPCs will have at least 16 CPUs per node.      //<![CDATA[<!--
